data.meta_site_name: Mental Health America of the Palm Beaches -
data.text:
We have created places for people to find belonging and purpose. Where they are defined by their talents and skills, not by a mental health diagnosis. And where everyone gets encouragement and support to grow and build a fulfilling life.

Here is where you belong.

“You will have the fulfillment, the help to get better, to make a better journey than you would have by yourself.” -Felicia, Fern Clubhouse Member
